             was indicted for <rs id="t18220220-183-off988" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-183-off988" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-183-off988" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220220-183-cd989" type="crimeDate">15th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-183-off988 t18220220-183-cd989"></join>, one flute, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220220-183-victim1672" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Truelove
                        <interp inst="t18220220-183-victim1672" type="surname" value="Truelove"></interp>
